    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《东方凋梦录 ～ Fading Illusion》是一部以东方Project世界观为背景的视觉小说，详细刻画了幻想乡以及幻想乡的人类和妖怪们。准备好与众多东方人气角色相遇，开启前往地底世界、幻想乡、天界乃至外界的旅程吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情梗概：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自古以来，过剩的好奇心往往伴随着惨痛的代价。人类曾凭借对未知的好奇而超越了动物，但这种好奇所引发的恐惧却催生了“妖怪”这种超越人类自身的生物。尽管人妖两族都找到了一套种族间和平共处的方法，但时至今日，谦德之道依然不是两族交往的主旋律。外界科技日新月异，幻想乡的贤者们却愈发沉浸在自我力量的幻觉中，未曾意识到可能存在某种异乎寻常的、深邃而浓密的事物，甚至连她们自己都不该去接触。日子一天天过去，其显现的可能性已逐渐成为时间问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵梦正在神社享受温暖的春日，不料八云紫打断了她的休憩。紫以她特有的方式从隙间中现身，给了灵梦一项紧急任务：让她去命莲寺的庆典上监视堇子的动向。事关博丽结界，灵梦别无选择，只好前往她竞争对手的基地，同时希望紫在晚上过来向她解释发生的一切……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>适合《东方Project》新人入坑！</strong>免费开玩的序章中有对东方设定的基本介绍，且游戏内设有可随时查看设定的词典。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/de2f4ba7e393cb8142b65f62d751c3e2.poster.avif?t=1759075274\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/de2f4ba7e393cb8142b65f62d751c3e2.webm?t=1759075274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/de2f4ba7e393cb8142b65f62d751c3e2.mp4?t=1759075274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>非线性剧情！</strong>游戏中有众多选择项，可导向截然不同的剧情。现阶段您可游玩「序章」、「贫乏之章」前三天的故事和「地底之章」第一天的故事，预计10-15小时游戏时间。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/e80c77ea33cf29b7c9feb42068e1100e.poster.avif?t=1759075274\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/e80c77ea33cf29b7c9feb42068e1100e.webm?t=1759075274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/e80c77ea33cf29b7c9feb42068e1100e.mp4?t=1759075274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游览东方Project的广袤世界！</strong>探索旧地狱、冥界、幻想乡各地，甚至更远的地方。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/72d97e09aafb34bc65c9b7f969ea39a4.poster.avif?t=1759075274\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/72d97e09aafb34bc65c9b7f969ea39a4.webm?t=1759075274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/72d97e09aafb34bc65c9b7f969ea39a4.mp4?t=1759075274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超过50位东方Project登场角色！</strong>其中肯定有你喜欢的人物。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/6da9706227dd242fbda33b19599919f7.poster.avif?t=1759075274\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/6da9706227dd242fbda33b19599919f7.webm?t=1759075274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132480/extras/6da9706227dd242fbda33b19599919f7.mp4?t=1759075274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
